h century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Agnes Curzon was born about 1296, in Tutbury, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom, her father, Stephen Curzon, was 28 and her mother, Joane Rollaston, was 24. She had at least 1 son with Sir Michael Nicholas de Burton. She died after 1350, in her hometown."},"et":{"Abt 1296–Aft 1350":"umbes 1296–pärast 1350","1296–1350":"1296–1350","1294–1339":"1294–1339","1327–1382":"1327–1382","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","1274–Female":"1274–Surnud","Abt 1296":"umbes 1296","1327":"1327","1274":"1274","1296":"1296","Aft 1350":"pärast 1350","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1294":"1294","1270":"1270","Abt 1327":"umbes 1327","1339":"1339","Tutbury, Staffordshire, England":"Tutbury, Staffordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1296–Aft 1350":"noin 1296–1350 jälkeen","1296–1350":"1296–1350","1294–1339":"1294–1339","1327–1382":"1327–1382","1270–Male":"1270–Kuollut","1274–Female":"1274–Kuollut","Abt 1296":"noin 1296","1327":"1327","1274":"1274","1296":"1296","Aft 1350":"1350 jälkeen","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1294":"1294","1270":"1270","Abt 1327":"noin 1327","1339":"1339","Tutbury, Staffordshire, England":"Tutbury, Staffordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1296–Aft 1350":"environ 1296–après 1350","1296–1350":"1296–1350","1294–1339":"1294–1339","1327–1382":"1327–1382","1270–Male":"1270–Décédé","1274–Female":"1274–Décédée","Abt 1296":"environ 1296","1327":"1327","1274":"1274","1296":"1296","Aft 1350":"après 1350","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1294":"1294","1270":"1270","Abt 1327":"environ 1327","1339":"1339","Tutbury, Staffordshire, England":"Tutbury, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Agnes Curzon est née environ 1296, à Tutbury, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Stephen Curzon, avait 28 ans et sa mère, Joane Rollaston, avait 24 ans. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Sir Michael Nicholas de Burton. Elle est déc